name: Outdoor Coffee Table
description: Simplicity is key with the Outdoor Coffee Table. The clean lines of the tabletop nod to classic mid-century design, placed upon silhouetted legs inspired by classic design. The solid teak wood has been treated to withstand outdoor conditions, but this coffee table would look just as good indoors. Style it with our Kangaroo Outdoor Lounge Chair or Kangaroo Outdoor Sofa.
